        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer130499212" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17472225374874727761">The best thing about this play is its subtlety. Throughout, the issue at hand is never explicitly said, however the audience can infer quite early on what the unnameable thing is, and that makes the dance around it that much more eloquent and haunting. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


