        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1947866459" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15278056636489517054">this extraordinary play asks a lot of moral questions but doesn&apos;t give you any answers. instead the author leaves it to the reader/ audience to continue the discussion long after the play ends.</span>
