<div id="review_3879884336" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3879884336" />
    <a title="Marina &amp;#x1f30a;" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/44432827-marina-x1f30a"><img alt="Marina &amp;#x1f30a;" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1642389615p2/44432827.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3879884336?book_show_action=true">Mar 08, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Marina &amp;#x1f30a;" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Marina &amp;#x1f30a;" href="/user/show/44432827-marina-x1f30a">Marina &amp;#x1f30a;</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3879884336" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5256827181162494567">There is a level of genius here that was put forth &amp; one I acknowledged &amp; found to be brilliant: uncertainty is the central theme to this entire story, and yet we as an audience, are left with this feeling that we share with the characters as we learn that doubt is a defining quality of our human existence. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


